Subject: Secunia Research: Microsoft PowerPoint File Path
	Handling Buffer Overflow

====================================================================== 

                     Secunia Research 09/02/2010

     - Microsoft PowerPoint File Path Handling Buffer Overflow -

====================================================================== 
Table of Contents

